These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
Pet: mouse, ferret, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. Pet:mouse is on the right of Pet:rabbit##1
2. Pet:ferret is somewhere between Pet:guinea-pig and Pet:rabbit##7
3. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left of Pet:ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | ferret | rabbit | mouse |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
