2. Food:radish is somewhere between Food:grapefruit and Food:avocado##7
3. Food:radish is between Food:grapefruit and Food:grapes##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | avocado | grapes | radish | grapefruit |

